NAME
       cursors - mouse cursors available in Tk


DESCRIPTION
       The -cursor widget option allows a Tk programmer to change
       the mouse cursor for  a  particular  widget.   The  cursor
       names recognized by Tk on all platforms are:
              X_cursor
              arrow
              based_arrow_down
              based_arrow_up
