PORTABILITY ISSUES
       Windows
              On  Windows  systems,  the  following  cursors  are
              mapped to native cursors:
                     arrow
                     center_ptr
                     crosshair
                     fleur
                     ibeam
                     icon
                     sb_h_double_arrow
                     sb_v_double_arrow
                     watch
                     xterm
              And the following additional cursors are available:
                     no
                     starting
                     size
                     size_ne_sw
                     size_ns
                     size_nw_se
                     size_we
                     uparrow
                     wait
              The  no  cursor  can  be specified to eliminate the
              cursor.


       Macintosh
              On Macintosh systems,  the  following  cursors  are
              mapped to native cursors:
                     arrow
                     cross
                     crosshair
                     ibeam
                     plus
                     watch
                     xterm
              And the following additional cursors are available:
                     text
                     cross-hair


